+# State test fixes test fixes
+
+**Package:** T10
+**Scope:** packages/state
+
+## Summary
+Updated stale state-manager tests to match the fixed account, contract-code, and storage semantics. Replaced live Optimism fork calls with deterministic mock fork transports so fork cache behavior is tested without network access. Refreshed stale error snapshots for the current package version.
+
+## Tests passing
+all
+
+## Tests still failing
+0
+
+## Changes
+- src/createStateManager.spec.ts:44 - Updated copy tests to use valid 20-byte addresses.
+- src/actions/modifyAccountFields.spec.ts:24 - Updated account field tests to use valid 20-byte addresses.
+- src/actions/originalStorageCache.spec.ts:12 - Updated cache test address to satisfy strict address validation.
+- src/actions/getAccount.spec.ts:9 - Added deterministic fork proof transport and canonical empty-account roots.
+- src/actions/getAccountFromProvider.spec.ts:6 - Replaced live fork provider call with a mocked eth_getProof transport.
+- src/actions/getProof.spec.ts:6 - Replaced live fork proof test setup with a mocked block/proof transport.
+- src/actions/getContractCode.spec.ts:13 - Replaced live bytecode fetches with mocked fork bytecode responses and exact byte assertions.
+- src/actions/getContractStorage.spec.ts:18 - Replaced live storage fetches with mocked fork proof/storage responses and updated remote storage expectations.
+- src/actions/__snapshots__/deepCopy.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated stale InternalError snapshot version.
+- src/actions/__snapshots__/generateCannonicalGenesis.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated stale InternalError snapshot version.
+- src/actions/__snapshots__/getContractStorage.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated stale storage-key error snapshot version.
+- src/actions/__snapshots__/putContractStorage.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated stale put-storage error snapshot versions.
