+# State test fixes test fixes
+
+**Package:** T10
+**Scope:** packages/state
+
+## Summary
+Updated stale state-manager tests to match the fixed account, contract-code, and storage semantics. Replaced live Optimism fork calls with deterministic mock fork transports so fork cache behavior is tested without network access. Refreshed stale error snapshots for the current package version.
+
+## Tests passing
+all
+
+## Tests still failing
+0
+
+## Changes
